headline.main: S.B. Penick 3d, 47, Psychiatrist And Medical Professor in Jersey

docs.lead_paragraph: Dr. Sydnor Barksdale Penick 3d, a psychiatrist who was a professor of internal medicine and psychiatry at the College of Medicine and Dentistry of New Jersey, died of a heart attack Sunday while playing tennis in Princeton, N.J. He was 47 years old and lived in Princeton.
